des: "Inspired by the Church Lady Martini. No vodka, so I guess it technically isn't a martini. I used the measures listed below for a small, delicious serving and all the flavors came through."
ins: Combine amaretto liqueur, coffee-flavored liqueur, raspberry-flavored liqueur, and ice cubes in a cocktail shaker. Cover, shake, and pour into a cocktail glass. Garnish with raspberries.
